  "text": "Volumetric estimates (mm [CITATION_1] ) of the cingulate substructures (i.e. ACC, MCC, and PCC) were then derived for each individual from data obtained from cortical reconstructions/ segmentation of MRI scans using the FreeSurfer image analysis suite (v 5.1, http://surfer.nmr.mgh.harvard.edu/), the technical details of which have been described in prior reports [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
